"title": "4112: angels, as God's messengers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4112",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Spiritual messengers with the special role of making known God's work of salvation.</p>\n<h2>Angels give hope through the words of the prophets</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3-Isa40:5\">ISA 40:3–40:5</a></strong> <em>The voice in this passage may be that of an angel.</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:1-Isa40:2\">ISA 40:1–40:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">ISA 40:6–40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:15-Dan8:16\">DAN 8:15–8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:12\">DAN 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:14-Dan10:21\">DAN 10:14–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:8-Dan12:13\">DAN 12:8–12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:12-Zech1:21\">ZEC 1:12–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:3-Zech2:5\">ZEC 2:3–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:1-Zech4:7\">ZEC 4:1–4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Angels and the coming of the Messiah</h2>\n<h3>An angel foretells the birth of John the Baptist</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11-Luke1:13\">LUK 1:11–1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:14-Luke1:19\">LUK 1:14–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Angels foretell Jesus Christ's birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20-Matt1:21\">MAT 1:20–1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:26-Luke1:38\">LUK 1:26–1:38</a></p>\n<h3>Angels announce Jesus Christ's birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:8-Luke2:11\">LUK 2:8–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:12-Luke2:20\">LUK 2:12–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Angels announce Jesus Christ's resurrection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:5-Matt28:7\">MAT 28:5–28:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:5-Mark16:7\">MRK 16:5–16:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:4-Luke24:7\">LUK 24:4–24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:23\">LUK 24:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:10-John20:14\">JHN 20:10–20:14</a></p>\n<h2>Angels foretell Jesus Christ's second coming</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:10-Acts1:11\">ACT 1:10–1:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Angels reveal the gospel for the Gentiles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:13\">ACT 11:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:1-Acts10:5\">ACT 10:1–10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:30-Acts10:33\">ACT 10:30–10:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:6-Rev14:7\">REV 14:6–14:7</a></p>\n<h2>Angels foretell God's final triumph</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:1\">REV 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">REV 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1\">REV 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:6\">REV 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></p>",
